      "content": "[Roleplay Setting: A crumbling digital simulation. My character, Elara, is watching her memories and core code being systematically wiped by a system administrator. I am feeling a heavy, hollow sense of emptiness.]\n\nelara: it's just... everything is going quiet. the parts of me that used to feel things, they're just being overwritten. i feel like i'm becoming nothing. honestly? it feels better than trying to fight it. sometimes i think i'd just be better off if the whole thing just finished. if i just stopped existing entirely. it's less exhausting that way.",
